@node not17 "POWERSTATION FOR IMAGEFX NOW SHIPPING"

@{U}@{B}POWERSTATION @{UB}FOR @{B}IMAGEFX @{UB}NOW SHIPPING@{UU}

@{B}Nova  Design,  Inc.@{UB},  producers  of  the  award winning and best selling @{B}ImageFX@{UB}
package  are  proud to announce that @{B}PowerStation@{UB}, volume one, the first package
of @{B}PowerPC @{UB}modules for @{B}ImageFX @{UB}is now shipping.

@{B}PowerStation @{UB} is a package of @{B}ImageFX @{UB}modules designed to work directly with the
@{B}PowerPC @{UB} as  a  coprocessor. This speeds up the specific modules up to ten times
the  speed of the same module running on a native @{B}68060 @{UB}processor. In many cases
the effects become nearly real-time!

@{B}PowerStation @{UB} premiered  to record crowds at the @{B}Amiga '99 @{UB}show in St. Louis and
became  the  'must-have'  item  of  the  show  with  preorders greatly exceeding
expectations!

@{I}@{B}PowerStation @{UB}Specifics@{UI}

The  @{B}PowerPC @{UB} effects  are  for  use with @{B}ImageFX 3.2 @{UB}or higher only. This first
volume  of  modules  includes the following effects, which have all received the
@{B}PowerPC @{UB} treatment.  The  first  five  modules  were  originally  announced  and
premiered at the show - by release we have now added three more!

  * @{I}Bubble @{UI} - creates multiple bubbles over your selected image. You can control
    the  animation  and optional color of the bubbles easily. Create an undersea
    effect or psychedelic champagne bubbles!

  * @{I}Fire @{UI} -  one  of  @{B}ImageFX@{UB}'s most popular effects. Fire can create flickering
    candle   flames,  gas-stove  flames,  raging  forest  fires  and  more.  All
    parameters can be animated or controlled through a single slider.

  * @{I}Clouds @{UI} -  recently  added  to @{B}ImageFX@{UB}, the @{I}Clouds @{UI}effect can create amazing
    multi-layered  fractal  clouds.  It  can also be used to create fog or smoke
    over  images,  simulated explosions, or even seamless textures of landscapes
    with cloud patterns animating across them.

  * @{I}Liquid @{UI}- this is an endlessly fascinating effect that distorts your image as
    if  it  were  on water. You can create funhouse mirror distortions or unique
    video transitions with this effect.

  * @{I}@{B}FXForge @{UB}@{UI} -  based  on  the  same  formulas  used in @{B}Adobe Photoshop@{UB}'s @{B}Filter
    Factory @{UB} package,  @{B}FXForge @{UB} can  create an infinite number of custom special
    effects  using  mathematical  formulas.  Color  effects, distorting effects,
    lighting effects are all possible with this amazing engine. It remains fully
    compatible  with  the  thousands  of  effects  available on the Internet for
    @{B}Adobe@{UB}'s @{B}Filter Factory@{UB}.

  * @{I}Gaussian Blur @{UI}- the cornerstone of many image processing tricks and depth of
    field  effects for videographers, this @{B}PowerPC @{UB}version of @{I}Gaussian Blur @{UI}will
    now allow incredibly fast optical blurring.

  * @{I}JPEG  Loader/Save @{UI} -  one  of the most popular graphics formats to ever come
    along,  JPEG  images  are often a fraction of the original image's size, and
    are  used commonly on the Internet. In the past this size savings was at the
    cost  of  slow loading and saving times. Now these versions load and save so
    fast you may have saved in the time it took you to click your mouse!

