You  can  order  via  1-800-IMAGE-69 in the US and Canada or call (804) 282-1157
elsewhere.  Orders can also be faxed to (804) 282-3768 or mailed to our address.
Anyone purchasing @{B}ImageFX 3.x @{UB}new after May 20th, 1999 can upgrade for free when
you mail us your dated proof of purchase with your upgrade request.

You'll  be  shipped @{B}ImageFX @{UB}and receive it in approximately four weeks depending
on  the  volume  of  preorders.  Previous  order  volumes have been high causing
delays, so order early!

@{B}ImageFX @{UB} is  also  available,  new,  through  your  favorite  @{B}Amiga @{UB} dealer at a
